text: Dominik Ferenčič (born 29 May 1996) is a Slovak footballer who currently plays for FC Rohožník as a forward. ==Club career== ===Spartak Myjava=== Ferenčič made his professional Fortuna Liga's debut for Spartak Myjava on 30 May 2015 against MFK Košice.SPARTAK MYJAVA VS.
